description: DEMOLITION OF EXISTING BUILDINGS AND ERECTION OF PART 26 AND PART 16 STOREYS TO PROVIDE 148 APARTMENTS (118 USE CLASS C3 AND 30 FLEXIBLE USE C1/C3) WITH 1800SQM OF FLEXIBLE RETAIL SPACE (CLASSES A1, A2, A3, A4) AT ST THOMAS ST AND LONDON BRIDGE ST (CONCOURSE) LEVELS, SERVICE AREA, THREE LEVELS OF BASEMENT INCLUDING CAP PARKING (28 SPACES) AND ASSOCIATED HARD AND SOFT LANDSCAPING, AMENITY SPACES AND ALTERATIONS TO EXISTING HIGHWAYS ADJOINING.
